Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,=============txt=============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.16,0:00:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你  你刚才说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在下与宗茂阁下是SEX过的关系是也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,三征西班牙不是也有转播么  直播的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,直接的！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\shad0\bord2\fs16}※生で(namade)日语里有生鲜的意思  可以指现场直播  也指无套直接的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  莫非是因为流血所以抵触到伦理规程了么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,还出血了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为最后在下贯穿了他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.37,0:00:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,次数的话大概50次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,50…宗茂大人被…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,为了洗刷丈夫的耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Arquebus·Cruz
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,十字炮火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:24.95,title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(481,271)}『容身之处的刀伤者』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,现在隐藏圣·马丁数量的把戏已经败露了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对方一定会转变为积极的攻击态势吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,全舰  仰角15度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,微速后退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,目标敌方主力舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,全舰  展开重力航行用外壁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,看来是向着主力舰队去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  我们也调头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,绕行至武藏后方进行追击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样把他们驱赶到主力舰队后方的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退战将不会成立  就会是我们的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  不会让你们得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前  得阻止机凰航母才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,燃烧吧  火焰！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧  魔球！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好球  打者出局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹啊  他还没有出局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是有备而来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,既然知道了就无须多言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是钱的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是钱的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是在这个战场中出场学生所有人的契约书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,内容是以工钱的1/10由我来支付作为代价
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,将战斗中行使的攻击力的1/10提供给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这攻击力都给了指弹么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,别小看棒球部！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我先警告你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,消失魔球的手法我已经明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,下一球就打下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹啊  这场胜负中没有保送哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样呢～！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是野挽大人输了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,投手直球接杀  出局
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥  你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们魔球的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Jud.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,隆包主将
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我们就只能到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,祝主将你们能有个良好的战果！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,敌方武神自武藏后方开始展开炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？干扰箔片好像变少了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,道征白虎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,大！朱雀要出击了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Jud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如今自动人形已可以进行干扰箔片的清扫工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还请铃大人在完成之前代为进行情报处理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,代行…什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会把外部情报输送进铃大人的感知系统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,并将其转为您可辨识的声音信息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是…世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,清  清秀的靠枕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,铃大人能全方位感知呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,方圆30公里  几乎全方位的感知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一点点也好  要削弱对方的炮击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,『拍手』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,想想神道术式究竟是为了什么而使用的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄准了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  是空包弹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊  吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈  大家都平安无事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不是什么可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我是梦魔  伊藤·健儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,今日  本着友好的目的  来到贵舰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,为了友好  在下稔侍怎能不尽一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好  one two one two  来来来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像造成了很不得了的后果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我们要干这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就算赢了也是和全世界为敌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那干脆…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要问为何而做…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,找不到那理由的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就去别的教导院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,能有别的地方可去的话  就是幸福了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  各位观众  我现在发布重大消息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,现在战局不理想的部分是不是很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说呢  发现这种地方的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我就会过去慰问你们哦  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧  不加油的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋就来捣乱咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,您真是国宝级的被讨厌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,笨啊  那是傲娇啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但战况依旧严峻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是单纯的缺人手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话  来帮忙了鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,犬鬼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  犬鬼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那个三七开眼睛男给的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是犬鬼居住的矿石哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,杂务就交给犬鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那就稍稍拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,出发了鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我  葵·托利和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,赫莱森·阿利亚达斯特就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不会逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所以虽然完不成的  想逃避的事多得数不清
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不过现在把那些「不可能」全部都交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,与之相对地  拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,请你们相信「我是做得到的」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Jud. 相信我们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,武藏的总长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,全员列队！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,准备！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗再开！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Judgement！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Jud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊  吾等乃领受圣罚之身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,吾等乃带走王的可能性和公主的感情之人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,然而吾等  亦乃不让王与公主悲伤之人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20}少得意了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这里可是在衰退啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是为了实现日不落而在努力的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就算灭亡我们也充满斗志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,日不落帝国向永无日出的亡国发出宣言！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,吾等无敌！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,三征西班牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,吾等必胜！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,三征西班牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,吾等荣光！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,三征西班牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He·Na·Re·S！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He·Na·Re·S！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He·Na·Re·S！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He·Na·Re·S！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Testament！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,英国舰队！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,尼古拉斯  使用一下国玺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要确认一下与极东交涉的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,「Save you from anything」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You这个词  也包含"你们"的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这样的话就没有违反约定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,去让霍华德把其他的船舰也派出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就如同当年的我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧  笨小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来宗茂大人的袭名解除令就能撤回了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什么！只有枪柄？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在此打扰是也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一条！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,两条！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这就叫得去做不习惯的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到竟然得使用与被宗茂大人击败时同样的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,同样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs16\pos(350,329)}Cuatro·cruz
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,贯穿吧「四角十字」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,起舞吧  抽成！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\shad0\bord2\fs16}※棒球术语  装出打算短打触击球的样子  突然切换成强打的奇袭战术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,单人打带跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一万元棒金！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,委拉大叔  快动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,圣谱显装「身坚的节制·新代」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,其效果是发动时将敌人的能力以使用次数进行分割
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,而我的「身坚的节制·旧代」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,则是将敌人的时间加倍延缓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  这样如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕  连自己人都一起遭殃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是武藏救援队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,将小生的慈善之举传达给三征西班牙的幼女们吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,来来  说吧  你想吃什么NE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那就给我份炒饭吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  给你咖喱NE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我说给我炒饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  给你炒饭NE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是咖喱吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你这蠢货  这下该怎么办啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,书记  快到时限了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  隆包  差不多到最后一局了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,本垒——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,打！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在里面垫了钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是在拖时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,只要发动了「身坚的节制·旧代」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,钱币落下的时间也变得更长了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那么就
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,速攻！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,淹没他吧  抽成！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,只能到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你们…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,主将！快前进  前进吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tes.！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,超震动破碎炮「咆吼列化」！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在右边！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那是在三河被击落武神上的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都知道朱雀的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:17:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  是直政决定要那么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  你也替她加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我会付报酬的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了  英国的猎犬和武藏的银狼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,『Tes.』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,『Bite』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,碍事！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,接招吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,别小看了副长啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最后一发了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好好给我接着吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,比赛结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,身为副长的我都放弃了怎么行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,三征西班牙还没结束呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,主将
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,比赛结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,给我击中  地摺朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,砸碎它  地摺朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,道征白虎  要将它卷进来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,村子遭到袭击的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,地摺朱雀却启动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那时  妹妹说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,明明她都快挺不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,却说「用我吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就用了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,起来吧  地摺朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,阻止它  道征白虎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,四圣…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,朱雀为了保护她而出手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,水…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不对  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,天空…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,宗茂阁下是如何击败这个敌人的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,连结吧  蜻蜓切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs16\pos(396,328)}Arquebus·Cruz
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,巨大的攻城武装「十字炮火」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,加上手上成对的双剑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,诚乃感人的夫妻恩爱是也！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Arquebus·Cruz
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,十字炮火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,连结吧  蜻蜓切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:21:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一把！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,两把！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,宗茂大人和这个女人就是平级了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\shad0\bord2\fs16\fad(200,0)}※誾采用了自愿解除武装的方式  以传达自己不愿承认二代与击败自己的宗茂平级的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.12,0:22:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,敌将  立花·誾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.14,0:22:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,被我击败了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.29,0:24:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,宗茂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.77,0:24:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.11,0:24:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,先榨干托利大人再说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.52,0:24:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前经常被赫莱森弄哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.04,0:24:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经决定好了 才不会有什么麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.94,0:24:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不是挺好嘛  去期望更多东西吧  赫莱森
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.52,0:24:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这便是  赫莱森的强欲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.10,0:24:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌「无法理解」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.84,0:24:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了你在期望着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.62,0:24:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,赫莱森就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.05,0:24:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一定要笑啊  赫莱森
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.06,0:24:22.02,title,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\shad2\bord0\fn方正宋三_GBK\fad(150,0)\pos(321,240)}『越境的耽欲者们』
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,=============ED=============
